<bibRefCitation author="Damgaard, J. &amp; Moreira, F. F. F. &amp; Weir, T. A. &amp; Zettel, H." box="[809,1057,1989,2014]" pageId="3" pagination="251 - 281" refId="ref8709" refString="Damgaard, J., Moreira, F. F. F., Weir, T. A. &amp; Zettel, H. (2014) Molecular phylogeny of the pond skaters (Gerrinae), discussion of the fossil record and a checklist of species assigned to the subfamily (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Gerridae). Insect Systematics and Evolution, 45, 251 - 281. https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 1876312 X- 44042105" type="journal article" year="2014">
